{"tid":1845152,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港交所取消周三新年首日開市儀式","createTime":"2020-01-27T03:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T10:52:55.000Z","uid":81228,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"88f4499121b8d8f85366d5ed9d68a2390007adfd","tid":1845152,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T03:59:10.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續擴散，港交所(00388)指出，考慮嘉賓及員工健康及安全後，決定取消原定於1月29日(初五)上午9時舉行的農曆新年首個交易日開市儀式。<br />\n<br />\n此外，香港金融服務界聯合舉辦2020新春酒會，在籌委會考慮後，亦宣布取消原定在2月5日傍晚舉行的活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=561935&amp;type=local\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fnews%2Fpost.php%3Fid%3D561935%26type%3Dlocal&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420Rv2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=bd23be2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=561935&amp;type=local</a>"},{"pid":"3a859309db8184c35e08d2cd82e6b542a10bf91f","tid":1845152,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:07:25.000Z","msg":"（取笑系列）抗爭者真係好垃圾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844940</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"83d3de30f3392eb05e6578a0bfa9b42ac7a1bcc6","tid":1845152,"uid":162015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:26:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2c9e8e63a6707eecaa405aef2616fce714f0739","tid":1845152,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:32:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"289ac6a2b66c430f81517875d561f102fea36061","tid":1845152,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:41:58.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0